# OS
.DS_Store

# ap2 runtime (when running the daemon in this tree). Intentionally
# does NOT exclude `.cc-autopilot/` — this repo is itself managed by ap2,
# so daemon-owned state files (progress.md, ideation_state.md, tasks/,
# insights/, cron.yaml, retry_state.json, operator_log.md) get committed
# alongside source. The runtime junk inside `.cc-autopilot/` (events.jsonl,
# daemon.pid, mm_state.json, debug/, …) is filtered by `.cc-autopilot/.gitignore`,
# which `ap2 init` writes.
TASKS.md.lock
